                Templum Liberi <lb n="2"/>Patris et Liberae vetus<lb break="no" n="3"/>tate dilabsum <note>sic</note> restituit <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ors</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Bel</abbr><ex>garum</ex></expan> adiectis por<lb break="no" n="5"/>ticibus curam agente <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Victore |(centurione) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> Severo et Pompeiano <lb n="8"/>II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tabula ansata. (B): Škegro: Z. 2-4 u. 7: geringfügige Leseabweichungen; Z. 9: Pisos. Textwiedergabe nach Atanacković-Salčić.</p>
